subject: OT: Apparently all my messages are spam
msgSnippet: Everyone: I apologize for the sudden flood of some old responses of mine. For some reason, Yahoo! groups SpamGuard assumes that many messages coming from me
messageBody:
Everyone:

I apologize for the sudden flood of some old responses of mine. For some
reason, Yahoo! groups' SpamGuard assumes that many messages coming from
me are spam. That's awesome, since I'm only the group's owner.

I have changed the necessary settings to avoid this problem in the
future. If we notice a sudden influx of spam, we'll deal with it somehow.

Take care.
--
